{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"639","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"科睿唯安全球百大創新機構，台灣居全球第4","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>記者林資傑／台北報導<span lang='EN-US'> 2020/02/20 08:01</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科睿唯安（<span lang='EN-US'>Clarivate Analytics</span>）發表<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年德溫特全球百大創新機構報告，台灣今年表現不凡，除了鴻海（<span lang='EN-US'>2317</span>）及工研院（<span lang='EN-US'>ITRI</span>）連<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>年入選外，廣達（<span lang='EN-US'>2382</span>）連<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>年入選、宏達電（<span lang='EN-US'>2498</span>）首度進榜，合計<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>家機構入選創下歷年最多，並與德國並列全球第<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>名。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科睿唯安指出，<span lang='EN-US'>2020</span>年德溫特全球百大創新機構遍布<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>大洲和<span lang='EN-US'>14</span>個國家地區，其中美國仍以<span lang='EN-US'>39</span>間稱冠、日本以<span lang='EN-US'>32</span>間居次，合計占據<span lang='EN-US'>71</span>％名額。就產業別觀察，硬體及電子產業以<span lang='EN-US'>38</span>間領先，年增<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>間，製造及醫療產業以<span lang='EN-US'>16</span>間居次，電信及軟體產業則各有<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>間。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告中指出，連<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>年、第<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>度獲選的工研院，仍在專利影響力及獲准率繳出亮眼表現，鴻海與廣達則持續在專利技術的國際化布局展現企圖心。宏達電過去於專利影響力上持續保有不錯成績，今年受惠國際化指標進步，成為首度躋身全球百大創新機構的關鍵。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科睿唯安大中華區德溫特與標準事業群總經理暨台灣區總經理范永銀表示，今年台灣共有<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>間機構入選，為發布報告以來入選最多的一次，顯見台灣優異的研發技術實力。期待未來能有更多的台灣機構，能在全球舞台上展現豐沛的研發創新能量與成果。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>今年報告首次將分析範圍拓展到前百大機構以外，並發現<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>大關鍵趨勢，包括前<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>千大機構在發明市場占有率縮水、協作的必要性、前段班日益壓縮。首先，越來越多專利是由較小規模的公司，甚至個人實業家或發明家所育成。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>其次，創新日益趨向知識密集，產生對更多元專業技術的需求。在德溫特世界專利索引中，每項專利列名發明人數平均值自<span lang='EN-US'>2014</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>2.84</span>人提升至<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>2.99</span>人。最後，而躋身德溫特全球百大創新機構的最低門檻，已於<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>年間增加<span lang='EN-US'>22</span>％。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科睿唯安表示，今年德溫特全球百大創新機構名單中，有藤倉（<span lang='EN-US'>Fujikura</span>）、宏達電、<span lang='EN-US'>Immersion</span>、超捷（<span lang='EN-US'>Microchip</span>）、施耐德電機（<span lang='EN-US'>Schneider Electric</span>）及騰訊等<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>間新進榜。上述機構自<span lang='EN-US'>2015</span>年以來平均排名上升<span lang='EN-US'>250</span>個名次，顯示均在高度競爭的創新市場中成功找到方向。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>科睿唯安也指出，全球創新環境正快速分散化，大型企業組織對全球發明的貢獻比重滑落至<span lang='EN-US'>18</span>％，顯示來自破壞式創新業者的挑戰日趨嚴峻。<span lang='EN-US'>IP</span>事業群分析部門負責人<span lang='EN-US'>Ed White</span>認為，大型機構未來若想繼續茁壯，必須開始探索並擁抱新的協作方式。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://m.ctee.com.tw/livenews/aj/20200220001102-260410</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-24","clk_count":"195"}},"__N_SSG":true}